  <title>
   <narrative xml:lang="EN">MW-2018 Promoting reading culture Malawi</narrative>
  </title>
  <description type="1">
   <narrative xml:lang="EN">The project goal is to achieve an enhanced reading culture and quality improvement in primary schools, Malawi. It will be implemented in 3 targeted Edukans STAR schools in Lilongwe. 
